Package cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dungeon_escape.model

Class GameItem

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.dungeon_escape.model.GameItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
Door, Enemy, InventoryItem, Platforms, Player
public class GameItem extends Object
The GameItem class represents a basic game object with position and visual representation. It serves as the base class for all interactive objects in the game world.

    • getBoundingBox

      public javafx.geometry.BoundingBox getBoundingBox()
      Gets the bounding box for collision detection. The bounding box is slightly smaller than the visual representation (20 pixels shorter on the y-axis) to provide better gameplay feel.
      Returns:
      A BoundingBox representing this item's collision area
